OL,3,CBlackpool's rough sleeping challenge:
OL,4,CWarm beds and rising numbers
OL,6,FWhen temperatures recently plummeted
OL,7,Fbelow freezing in Blackpool, it
OL,8,Ftriggered a critical lifeline.
OL,10,FThe town's Severe Weather Emergency
OL,11,FProtocol (SWEP) was activated -
OL,12,Fmeaning that for a few nights at
OL,13,Fleast, those sleeping rough were
OL,14,Fbrought inside and shielded from the
OL,15,Felements.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/14
