OL,3,CBlackpool's rough sleeping challenge:
OL,4,CWarm beds and rising numbers
OL,6,FHelping Hearts was one of the
OL,7,Fcharities delivering services on the
OL,8,Fground through a temporary night
OL,9,Fshelter, granting ITV Granada rare
OL,10,Faccess to see what happens behind the
OL,11,Fscenes.
OL,13,FIt was 8pm when we arrived. The doors
OL,14,Fweren't due to open for another hour,
OL,15,Fbut people were already beginning to
OL,16,Ftrickle in.
OL,18,FVolunteers unfolded beds and prepared
OL,19,Ffood. The aim, they stressed, wasn't
OL,20,Fjust to provide shelter.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
