OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772204160
OL,3,CBlackpool's rough sleeping challenge:
OL,4,CWarm beds and rising numbers
OL,6,F"We want to bolster their self-esteem
OL,7,Fand self-respect," Jo Kember
OL,8,Fexplained. A trustee of the charity
OL,9,Fand a former architect, she began
OL,10,Fvolunteering after taking early
OL,11,Fredundancy.
OL,13,FThat support, she said, comes from
OL,14,Fsimple things - sitting and eating
OL,15,Ftogether, playing games, creating
OL,16,Froutine.
OL,18,F"When people come here, it's to stop
OL,19,Fthem from literally freezing to death
OL,20,Fon the streets," said Andrew Mills,
OL,21,Fthe charity's CEO.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@RO]zD@AOU|D@PO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/14
