CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772204160
OL,3,CBlackpool's rough sleeping challenge:
OL,4,CWarm beds and rising numbers
OL,6,F"It has a massive impact for them
OL,7,Fbecause it's warm and safe - and
OL,8,Fthat's the key thing."
OL,10,FOne by one, guests began to arrive.
OL,11,FThe shelter was far from home, but it
OL,12,Fwas a place of safety - and on a night
OL,13,Flike that, it was enough.
OL,15,FDarren Mander has spent the past three
OL,16,Fmonths sleeping rough following a
OL,17,Fmarriage breakdown. The "atrocious
OL,18,Fweather" he said, had made life even
OL,19,Fharder.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@VO]yD@YOUzD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/14
