OL,3,CBlackpool's rough sleeping challenge:
OL,4,CWarm beds and rising numbers
OL,6,F"It's so cold. I'm trying to keep warm
OL,7,Fat night with the wind and the rain
OL,8,Fespecially," he said.
OL,10,F"My tent's not the best and it leaks,
OL,11,Fso I've been hanging my sleeping bag
OL,12,Fout to dry every day."
OL,14,FDarren describes the conditions he has
OL,15,Ffaced while living in a tent on the
OL,16,Fstreet
OL,18,FChris Brady described similar
OL,19,Fconditions.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@VO]
