PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772204160
OL,3,CBlackpool's rough sleeping challenge:
OL,4,CWarm beds and rising numbers
OL,6,F"I'm waking up in the middle of the
OL,7,Fnight drenched, freezing - and I'm
OL,8,Ftalking cold. You can even get burns
OL,9,Fon you, it's that cold," he told me.
OL,11,FThe charity opened its doors to 12
OL,12,Fpeople on the night we were there.
OL,13,FEvery one of them, Andrew explained,
OL,14,Fwas known to the council.
OL,16,F"They'll come in and chat to people
OL,17,Fand try to find a longer-term
OL,18,Fsolution," he said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOUzD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/14
