OL,3,CBlackpool's rough sleeping challenge:
OL,4,CWarm beds and rising numbers
OL,6,FBut in reality, the council operates
OL,7,Fwithin a tightly defined legal
OL,8,Fframework. While emergency shelter can
OL,9,Fbe offered during severe weather,
OL,10,Flonger-term housing duties depend on
OL,11,Fstatutory tests, including whether
OL,12,Fsomeone has a recognised local
OL,13,Fconnection to the area.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
