OL,3,CBlackpool's rough sleeping challenge:
OL,4,CWarm beds and rising numbers
OL,6,FRough sleepers with no established
OL,7,Flink to Blackpool may be accommodated
OL,8,Ffor one night under the Severe Weather
OL,9,FEmergency Protocol before being
OL,10,Freconnected to an area where they do
OL,11,Fhave a recognised local connection,
OL,12,Fwhere appropriate cold weather
OL,13,Fprovision is expected to be in place.
OL,15,FThe threshold for what is known as
OL,16,F"priority need" also remains high.
OL,17,FHouseholds with dependent children and
OL,18,Fpeople deemed severely vulnerable are
OL,19,Fmore likely to qualify for a full
OL,20,Fhousing duty.
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/14
