OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772204160
OL,3,CBlackpool's rough sleeping challenge:
OL,4,CWarm beds and rising numbers
OL,6,FFor many single adults without
OL,7,Fdocumented vulnerabilities, the
OL,8,Fcouncil's ability to secure permanent
OL,9,Faccommodation is limited - shaped by
OL,10,Flegislation as well as the
OL,11,Favailability of housing stock.
OL,13,FAndrew Mills, CEO of Helping Hearts,
OL,14,Fexplains why their service is so vital
OL,16,FGovernment figures released 26
OL,17,FFebruary show rough sleeping has hit a
OL,18,Frecord high - both nationally and
OL,19,Fregionally.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
