PN,39712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772204160
OL,3,CBlackpool's rough sleeping challenge:
OL,4,CWarm beds and rising numbers
OL,6,FIn response to the figures, the
OL,7,Fgovernment's Homelessness Minister,
OL,8,FAlison McGovern said: "There are
OL,9,Fsimply too many people facing life on
OL,10,Fthe streets or in temporary
OL,11,Faccommodation. While the statistics
OL,12,Fshow progress in some areas, it is
OL,13,Fclearly not good enough.
OL,15,F"We are investing a record #3.6bn
OL,16,Ffunding to tackle homelessness,
OL,17,Fincluding #50m announced today to help
OL,18,Fcouncils and voluntary groups often on
OL,19,Fthe front line of helping the most
OL,20,Fvulnerable people and creating real
OL,21,Fchange for those that need it most.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
