FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772204160
OL,3,CBlackpool's rough sleeping challenge:
OL,4,CWarm beds and rising numbers
OL,6,F"We are reducing the worst forms of
OL,7,Ftemporary accommodation with ongoing
OL,8,Freductions of children in B&Bs.
OL,10,F"Our recently published National Plan
OL,11,Fto End Homelessness recognises the
OL,12,Fscale of the crisis with bold action
OL,13,Fto prevent homelessness before it
OL,14,Foccurs and make sure everyone has the
OL,15,Fsafe, secure home that they deserve."
OL,17,FBack in Blackpool, as snow began to
OL,18,Ffall outside, it was lights out. By
OL,19,F7.30 the following morning, breakfast
OL,20,Fwas already under way.
OL,26,@rD@AOUwD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/14
