OL,3,CBlackpool's rough sleeping challenge:
OL,4,CWarm beds and rising numbers
OL,6,FThe building had to be cleared by
OL,7,F8.30am to make way for a Sunday
OL,8,Fschool, and guests filtered back onto
OL,9,Fthe streets. The shelter did not
OL,10,Freopen the following night because the
OL,11,Ffreeze had lifted - but the need had
OL,12,Fnot.
OL,14,FWant more on the issues effecting the
OL,15,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,16,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,17,Four region.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/14
